{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemeradiobuttoncomponenttokensprovider"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeRadioButtonComponentTokensProvider"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"component  tokens of radio button","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" for  "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"radios","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" objects"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSRadioButton"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSRadioButtonItem"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllRadioButtonComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide all tokens to the users."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeRadioButtonComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"RadioButtonComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"radio buttons"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Radio buttons","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of sizes (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SizeSemanticToken"},{"type":"text","text":") and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"borders ("},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"BorderRadiusSemanticToken"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"BorderWidthSemanticToken"},{"type":"text","text":")."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"These components share the same type of tokens which are all gathered here."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange"]]},"relationshipsSections":[{"kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/AllRadioButtonComponentTokensProvider","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/19OUDSTokensComponent011RadioButtonB6TokensP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s8CopyableP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/TokensProvider"],"type":"conformsTo"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeRadioButtonComponentTokensProvider"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Overview","type":"heading","anchor":"overview"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Define your own provider for radio button component tokens","    \/\/ by inheriting from existing provider","    class CustomRadioButtonComponentTokensProvider: OrangeThemeRadioButtonComponentTokensProvider {","","        \/\/ Then override the radio button component tokens you want.","","        override var sizeMinWidth: SizeSemanticToken { sizes.iconWithLabelLargeSizeXl }","","        override var borderWidthSelected: BorderWidthSemanticToken { borders.widthThin }","","        \/\/ ...","    }","","    \/\/ Or define your own provider from scratch","    class CustomRadioButtonComponentTokensProvider: RadioButtonComponentTokens {","","        \/\/ And implement hundreds of tokens.","        \/\/ You are allowed to give semantic tokens providers if you want to define values.","    }"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Then, you can give this "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CustomRadioButtonComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" to your own theme implementation:"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["class LocalTheme: OrangeTheme {","","    override init() {","        super.init(radioButton: CustomRadioButtonComponentTokensProvider())","    }","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"or to an already existing theme for example:"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    OrangeTheme(radioButton: CustomRadioButtonComponentTokensProvider())"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is also possible to use your own semantic tokens providers for this component tokens providers:"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Uses by default here:","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSizeSemanticTokensProvider for sizes","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeBorderSemanticTokensProvider for borders","    let radioButtonComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeRadioButtonComponentTokensProvider()","","    \/\/ Or use your own size, border, color and opacity semantic tokens providers (or only some)","    let radioButtonComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeRadioButtonComponentTokensProvider(","                                                sizes: CustomSizeSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                           